    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（CMが話題になったおかげで、バレンタイン前日の）\n（トリエルは取材やテレビ出演と大忙しだな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Thanks to the CM becoming a hot topic‚ the day before Valentine's Day…）\n（TRINITYAiLE is busy with interviews and TV shows…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.3666666746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "CM撮影の裏話ですか？\nみんな笑顔で和気あいあいとした楽しい現場でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Talking about behind-the-scenes of the CM shoot?\nEveryone was smiling‚ and it was a fun and friendly set.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.6000000079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.0333333413
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "みんな制服でえらい可愛くて……え？\nCMにはキスシーンがあるいう噂があったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They all looked cute in their uniforms… Huh?\nThere were rumors of a kissing scene in the CM?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.5000000079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.3666666746
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "なんのことやら、うちにはさっぱり分からへんねぇ\nふふふ、ほな次の話題いきましょか～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have no idea what you're talking about.\nHaha‚ well then‚ let's move on to the next topic.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.7666666746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（優のやつ、司会者に笑顔で圧をかけてるぞ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Yu's really putting pressure on the host with that smile…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.1333333413,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.6666666746
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "バレンタインの予定ですか？　せやなぁ……\n今年は好きな人に本命チョコをあげたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ any plans for Valentine's Day?\nI'd like to give Valentine's chocolates to someone special this year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.3666666746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "なーんて、本命チョコをあげる相手なんていません\n今は恋よりもアイドル活動に夢中ですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just kidding‚ there's no one I want to give chocolates to.\nRight now‚ I'm more focused on being an idol than romance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.8666666746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.0666666746
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "そういう意味やと、うちの本命は\nいつも応援してくれるファンのみんなやね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that sense‚ my special someone is\nall the fans who always support me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.4333333413,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（恋愛の話題をはぐらかしつつファンにアピール……）\n（いつもながら優のトーク力は頼りになるな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She's avoiding the topic of romance and appealing to the fans…）\n（As always‚ Yu's talking skills are reliable…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.9666666746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.4000000079
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（さてと、番組が終わったらすぐ次の現場に移動だ）\n（時間もないし、今のうちにタクシーを呼んでおくか）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Well then‚ once the show's over‚ it's off to the next shoot…）\n（I don't have much time‚ so should I call a taxi now?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.2666666746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "はい、ありがとうございました\nいっぱいお喋り出来て楽しかったわぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you very much.\nIt was fun talking a lot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.3333333413,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.8666666746
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "明日はトリエルのバレンタインライブがあります\n配信もあるので、番組を見てるみなさんも観に来てな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tomorrow is TRINITYAiLE's Valentine's live performance.\nWe also have an online stream‚ so everyone come see us!",
        "id": ""
      },
