      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.5666651487
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "今日はスケジュールがタイトやからしゃあないわぁ\nこのまま次の現場に直行するんやろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today's schedule is tight‚ so it can't be helped.\nAre we heading straight to the next shoot from here?",
