      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "到着や～。時間ぴったりやわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We've arrived. Right on time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.7333302895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃ、俺は別の現場に行かなきゃいけないから\n後のことは頼んだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I have to head to another shoot‚ so…\nI'll leave the rest to you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.5999969561,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya",
      "startTime": 128.3999969561
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "任せて下さい\nしっかりPRイベントを盛り上げてみせます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Leave it to me.\nI'll make sure to liven up the PR event.",
