      "text": "……行ったか\nさて、俺も急いで次の現場に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…They're gone.\nWell‚ I should hurry to the next shoot…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.0333272377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　座席に荷物が置きっぱなしじゃないか\nこの荷物は確か……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? There's a bag left on the seat.\nI think this bag belongs to…",
        "id": ""
      },
